### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@productId = 4b5c6d7e-8f90-4123-a4b5-c6d7e8f90123
@reviewId = e5f6a7b8-c9d0-4e5f-9a0b-1c2d3e4f5a6b
@userId = 6d5e4f3a-2b1c-4d0e-9f1a-2b3c4d5e6f7a

### Get reviews for a product with pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reviews/{{productId}}?PageNumber=1&PageSize=5
Accept: application/json

### Submit a new review for a product
# @name createReview
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reviews/{{productId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Absolutely love these headphones! The noise cancellation is incredible and the battery life lasts through my entire workday."
}

### Submit a review without comment (rating only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reviews/{{productId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 4
}

### Analyze product reviews with AI with Normal orchestration mode
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reviews/{{productId}}/analyze?AgentOrchestrationType=Normal
Accept: application/json

### Analyze product reviews with AI with Sequential orchestration mode
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reviews/{{productId}}/analyze?AgentOrchestrationType=Sequential
Accept: application/json

### Analyze product reviews with AI with GroupChat orchestration mode
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reviews/{{productId}}/analyze?AgentOrchestrationType=GroupChat
Accept: application/json

### Analyze product reviews with AI with HandOff orchestration mode
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reviews/{{productId}}/analyze?AgentOrchestrationType=Handoff
Accept: application/json

### Analyze product reviews with AI
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reviews/{{productId}}/analyze
Accept: application/json


### Get review trends and patterns (last 30 days)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reviews/{{productId}}/trends?DaysBack=30
Accept: application/json

### Get review trends for last 90 days
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reviews/{{productId}}/trends?DaysBack=90
Accept: application/json

### Compare multiple products by reviews
# @name compareProducts
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reviews/compare
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productIds": [
    "3a4b5c6d-7e8f-4012-93a4-b5c6d7e8f901",
    "5c6d7e8f-9012-4234-b5c6-d7e8f9012345",
    "6d7e8f90-1234-4345-c6d7-e8f901234567"
  ]
}

### Get AI-generated quality summary for a product
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reviews/{{productId}}/quality-summary
Accept: application/json